The temple of Athena has been abandoned, left to sink in
the swamps of Araakas, and the symbol of Athena's power has 
crumbled with time. Find the temple, locate the remains of 
the statue of Athena and rebuild it, so a force of good may 
stand against the Arch-lich Araakas. The statue of Athena 
will not be complete until her eyes are returned and she can 
see again.

This is a medium to high level quest, and requires much exploration.
